                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=cgmartin",
                        "name": "cgmartin",
                        "displayName": "Chris Martin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Understood. Thank you for reviewing. \r\n\r\nYes perhaps some kind of registry attached to zend_app that the application resources can interact with to access these types of shared objects.\r\n",
